    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/InventoryView.tsx`. It will represent the detailed corporate stockpile and raw materials inventory, including:\n- Interactive filters (live search input, category selection, and inventory status checkboxes/dropdowns).\n- A high-density data table with **manual stock adjustments** (+ / -) to change quantity. When stock drops below 500 units, the system dynamically marks the item as \"Low Stock\" and triggers warning indicators in real-time.\n- An **Active Alerts Panel** detailing raw materials in a critical state, paired with a quick action button \"Automate Reorder\" to instantly deploy automated replenishments and update the corporate ledgers."
