  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Reviewing Project Milestones**\n\nI\'m pleased to report the development server restarted successfully! I\'ve been reviewing achievements and noting the progress. I have updated `metadata.json` with a specific descriptive name and a clear capability definition. I\'ve also constructed a robust, fully fledged full-\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed the full-stack, AI-powered **Cloud ERP System** with responsive screen layouts, custom interactive components, and server-side Gemini intelligence. \n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual & Design Concept\n- **Cloud Slate Theme**: A clean, high-contrast corporate canvas with deep charcoal text, generous negative spacing, and sharp slate-blue accents.\n- **Micro-Animations**: Staggered page entrances, hover feedback on ledger rows, spinning icons, and spring-physics visual tabs managed by the `motion` library.\n- **Responsive Navigation**: A standard $280\\text{px}$ sidebar for desktops, paired with an elegant, spring-animated slide-out hamburger drawer for tablets and mobile viewports.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\233\240\357\270\217 Core Functional Modules\n\n1. **Dashboard & Executive Command Center** (`DashboardView.tsx`)\n   - **Financial Trends Chart**: A high-fidelity, interactive SVG line and bar visualization of Monthly Revenue vs. Expenses with reactive state tooltips.\n   - **Warehouse Distribution Chart**: A dynamic SVG donut chart mapping raw stock divisions across active logistics zones.\n   - **Smart Actions Simulator**: Instant operational controls to hire machine learning personnel, approve finance invoices, and design workflow pipelines.\n   - **Nexus AI Chat Center**: An embedded chat module communicating with the Express backend to evaluate stockpile constraints, suggest action plans, and simulate corporate scheduling using the `gemini-3.5-flash` model.\n\n2. **Operations & Analytics** (`AnalyticsView.tsx`)\n   - **AI Projections Simulator**: An interactive financial modeling card with a range slider allowing executives to simulate future growth targets (5% to 100%) and instantly compute projected revenues and net profit curves backed by localized advisory recommendations.\n   - **Departmental Budget Ledger**: A high-density audit matrix indicating personnel counts, budget allocations, actual expenditures, and division-specific ROI safety tags.\n\n3. **Inventory & Stockpile** (`InventoryView.tsx`)\n   - **SKU Search & Category Filters**: Multi-variable filters tracking items and stockpiles in real-time.\n   - **Manual Stock Controls**: Incremental quantity adjustments ($+$ and $-$ buttons) that dynamically trigger \"Low Stock\" alerts if warehouse supplies fall below the company safety margin of $500$ units.\n   - **Automatic Replenishment Pipeline**: A quick-action button that triggers cargo logistics requests to top up raw material levels.\n\n4. **Production Pipelines** (`ProductionView.tsx`)\n   - **Kanban Board Layout**: A Trello-style manufacturing pipeline with active cards grouped by stage (*Backlog, Scheduled, In Progress, Quality Control, Completed*).\n   - **Stage Advancements**: An interactive step button to move manufacturing batches across columns, generating real-time system activities and updating progress metrics.\n   - **Batch Scheduler**: A sidebar form allowing administrators to log target product names, schedule unit quantities, assign priority flags, and set timelines.\n\n5. **Global Supply Chain** (`SupplyChainView.tsx`)\n   - **Carrier Cargo Tracking**: Grid entries charting transit routes, global suppliers, and estimated unloading timelines.\n   - **Milestone Timelines**: A visual progress track representing cargo stages from contract signing to warehouse docks.\n\n6. **ERP Configurations** (`SettingsView.tsx`)\n   - **Base Ledger Currency Selector**: Adjusting the base currency (USD, EUR, GBP, JPY) instantly updates and formats all KPI values across the dashboard and tables.\n   - **AI Hyper-Parameters Console**: Real-time sliding controls for Gemini temperature coefficients, preferred model choices, and core system instructions.\n   - **API Secrets Monitor**: A status detector that verifies workspace secrets, accompanied by a step-by-step setup guide.\n\n---\n\n### \360\237\224\222 Enterprise Server Architecture (`server.ts`)\n- **Server-Side API Proxy**: Keeps sensitive API keys protected within the secure server runtime.\n- **Graceful Sandboxing**: If a personal API key is missing, the backend seamlessly flags warning alerts in the chat UI and loads high-fidelity simulation fallbacks, ensuring there are no startup crashes or disrupted work sessions.\n- **Uptime Binding**: Securely configured on Node port `3000` for production container pipelines."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 2
      nanos: 51294923
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
